text: Helle Panzieri (born 31 March 1972) is an Italian-born Danish taekwondo martial artist. She competed at the 1992 Summer Olympics, where taekwondo was a demonstration sport, in the finweight event. At the European Taekwondo Championships she won the bronze medal in 1990 and 1992. == References == == Other websites == * Category:1972 births
